snippet.title: LetsTalk: Domestic Abuse Johnny Depp and Amber Heard
snippet.description:
#ABUSE #STOPABUSE #DOMESTICABUSE #DOMESTICVIOLENCE  #ANTI-ABUSE #ENDDOMESTICVIOLENCE #ENDABUSE
Welcome back family, this video is about domestic violence in a relationship. I have been following Johnny Depp and his ex wife Amber Heard story about their abusive relationship. I am so happy hearing and seeing more people speaking out about their abusers. I am one person who take this topic very strongly and it hurt deeply when people don't or can't speak out. Let's put a stop to ABUSE, let's ENDABUSE.
